@andrewcmyers it looks like there are some bugs in the GPU build, e.g.

https://ci.tensorflow.org/job/tensorflow-pull-requests-gpu/6226/consoleFull
```
ERROR: /workspace/tensorflow/java/BUILD:194:1: Building tensorflow/java/ConstantTest.jar (1 source file) failed: Worker process sent response with exit code: 1.
tensorflow/java/src/test/java/org/tensorflow/op/core/ConstantTest.java:51: warning: [rawtypes] found raw type: Tensor
      Tensor result = sess.runner().fetch(op.asOutput()).run().get(0);
      ^
  missing type arguments for generic class Tensor<T>
  where T is a type-variable:
    T extends Object declared in class Tensor
tensorflow/java/src/test/java/org/tensorflow/op/core/ConstantTest.java:53: warning: [unchecked] unchecked call to <U>copyTo(U) as a member of the raw type Tensor
      assertArrayEquals(ints, result.copyTo(actual));
                                           ^
...
```
